docDescription: Alex Carry is a Anesthesiologist specialist with 10 years of experience
serviceDescription: Anesthesiology is the branch of medicine dedicated to pain relief for patients before, during, and after surgery.

docDescription: Alex Carry is a Dermatology specialist with 10 years of experience
serviceDescription: Dermatologists are physicians who treat adult and pediatric patients with disorders of the skin, hair, nails, and adjacent mucous membranes.

docDescription: Marry is a specialist Surgeon with 8 years of experience
serviceDescription: General surgeons provide a wide variety of life-saving surgeries, such as appendectomies and splenectomies. They receive broad training on human anatomy, physiology, intensive care, and wound healing.

docDescription: Jayed is a Neurologist with 5 years of experience
serviceDescription: Neurologists are doctors who diagnose and treat problems with the brain and nervous system. They don't do surgery. Your doctor might recommend that you see one if they think you have an illness that needs expert care.

docDescription: Ronald is a Urologist with 10 years of experience
serviceDescription: Urology is the health care segment that cares for the male and female urinary tract, including kidneys, ureters, bladder, and urethra.

docDescription: Neil has over 20 years of experience as a Cardiologist
serviceDescription: A cardiologist specializes in diagnosing and treating diseases of the cardiovascular system. The cardiologist will carry out tests, and they may perform some procedures, such as heart catheterizations, angioplasty, or inserting a pacemaker..
